<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>西安市胸科医院获得两项荣誉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200908/32aceba9780f44a9bd28024d2ebf3e86.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
