➜粉笔无言写春秋，一首情诗颂师恩
http://www.sohu.com/a/417105555_100185418	38841
<p>那位包容我们所有叛逆</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">耐心教导我们的老师</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在三尺讲台上</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">倾其所有</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">铺就我们求知的道路</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">转眼间教师节即将来临</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">心中纵有千言万语</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">却又不知从何说起</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">动人的话</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">也许千言万语</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">也许......</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200908/697aa862448445dfa36986228e2c1e3e.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>致徐礼鲜老师——关华</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">师尊六旬胜少年，强国初心似海深；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">辛勤耕耘三尺台，愿作人梯为人仁。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甘乳一生育英才，才俊辈出树茂森；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">破茧成蝶师生情，九洲桃李报师恩。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200908/5036d148797446b6b290a8ca9d907658.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
